r a childhood obesity reduction plan, it is essential to assess the effectiveness of these existing programs and seek ways to improve or optimize their impact before committing new resources. This approach will help ensure that investments are directed towards interventions with proven benefits and contribute to the overall goal of reducing childhood obesity in Wales.">
