uality of Packed Lunches:&#10;&#09;* Encourage awareness and education among parents about the importance of nutritious food in packed lunches.&#10;&#09;* Offer resources and support for parents to make healthier choices, without implementing strict regulations on packed lunch contents (Janet Finch-Saunders AM).&#10;4. Role of Parental Policing:&#10;&#09;* A balance should be struck between encouraging healthy choices and respecting parental autonomy over their children's meals (Janet Finch-Saunders AM).&#10;&#09;* Encouraging partnerships between schools, Public Health Wales, and local communities to drive population-level approaches to promoting healthier food choices in packed lunches (Dr Frank Atherton).">
