uch as active lessons or brain breaks, to create an environment that encourages and promotes regular movement and exercise throughout the day.&#10;6. Train teachers to incorporate movement into their teaching methods and provide adequate space and equipment for physical education classes and recess, making it fun, accessible, and part of the daily routine for all students.">
